"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1933348-olympics-2024-Andy-Macdonald-Team-GB-skateboarder-51\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Andy Macdonald brought the crowd, including skateboarding legend Tony Hawk, to their feet during the men's preliminary round at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"score\": 0.9999978194979248, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Macdonald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the judges less so, with Macdonald finishing 18th in the qualifying rounds - a decision that sparked fury in the stands.\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboarding fans packed into the Place de la Concorde arena were unhappy the 51-year-old wasn't rewarded for his stellar showing.\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 0.9999999999599822, \"rank\": 4.0102067768435506e-11, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The father of three was able to see the positives though, with the skateboarding legend telling theBBC: \\\"That's how you are supposed to do it.\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You get your run down and then you build on it, everything after that is just a bonus.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The last run was just a bonus.\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a round marred by errors, with severa